.Xr sigaction 2 ,
.Xr sigsuspend 2 ,
.Xr sigvec 2 ,
.Xr sigblock 2 ,
.Xr sigsetops 3
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
function call appeared in
.Bx 4.2
and has been deprecated.
